	<simplesect id="tools_browser_view_contextmenu_advanced_copyascsv">
		<title>Advanced > Copy Entry as CSV</title>
		<para>
			Copies the selected entries in CSV format. By default the
			tabulator is
			used as attribute delimiter, a pipe is used as
			value delimiter and
			each attribute is wrapped by
			double-quotes, these settings could be
			changed in
			<link linkend="preferences_text_formats">
				Text Formats preferences
			</link>
